title nasim — VCS-02 INSERT Commit

' Participants with box colors per C4 layer

note over participants
  Scope:          Git commit creation with conventional format
  Preconditions:  Files staged, commit message valid
  Excludes:       Status checking (VCS-01), diff (VCS-03)
  Contexts:       Auto-commit after edits, manual commit requests
  Rollback:       Reset HEAD if commit fails mid-operation
  Design:         Atomic commit with pre-commit hook validation
end note

== VCS-02 INSERT Commit ==

AgentOrchestrator -> GitCommit: commit(message, files)
GitCommit -> GitStatus: check_staged()
GitStatus --> GitCommit: staged_files
GitCommit -> GitCommit: validate_message(message)
GitCommit -> GitCommit: git commit -m message
GitCommit --> AgentOrchestrator: commit_result(hash, files)

note over participants
  Flow:    Check staged -> validate message -> commit -> return hash
  State:   validating -> committing -> committed
  Failure: Pre-commit hook fails -> abort, return error
  Success: Agent receives commit hash and file list
end note

@enduml